text:
Huh?
Oh, hold on a moment...!
Sorry, you must have been changing, weren't you?

Bullseye!
Yeah, sorry for having you wait outside.

It's no big deal...
Better than than to walk in by accident...
An idol producer... peeking into the dressing room...
Hey, this is no laughing matter!

"How could such an upright man do such a thing..."
I'd be like that.

Of course, you can count on me not to do that!
──It's not gonna happen...!
